{"tid":337420,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟係咪鐘意左佢","createTime":"2017-07-27T09:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T20:52:08.000Z","uid":70777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b91abeaf54e033bb8fee4502c8de5db13bd8a9","tid":337420,"uid":70777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:57:41.000Z","msg":"前排突然間同個人突然之間熟左<br />\n大家又覺得幾啱傾 所以有時會傾下電話咁<br />\n漸漸變左好似會好期待佢打來 <br />\n搞到我唔知自己係純粹慣左有佢陪同係鐘意左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我咁大個人都無戀愛經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係好知中意一個人係咩感覺(可能以前鐘意過人都唔知自己鐘意佢<br />\n<br />\n而家好煩 完全唔知自己係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人可以比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbef1c19b3b6240841f23189e367e82d3ee6d3df","tid":337420,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:59:03.000Z","msg":"YES"},{"pid":"ab007a75009677a797b4a10d087394bba91131db","tid":337420,"uid":70777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>YES</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我唔會純粹係中意同佢傾計咋咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192179965cf5cb10c8335d3b740a8141b8959601","tid":337420,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>YES</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我唔會純粹係中意同佢傾計咋咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n又唔係叫你同佢結婚"},{"pid":"8ee13e0bebd168e9d67bfaadb92f0a29d06924c2","tid":337420,"uid":56567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:09:36.000Z","msg":"yer"},{"pid":"c2ccec146349185e88f6e9e46b4f3894f4b7bcf2","tid":337420,"uid":56567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:10